snippet.title: ACME Restorations
snippet.description:
Hi and thanks for checking out my channel. I've been restoring tools and machines for years.
Restoration projects are mostly tool and machine restorations, possibly some vintage or retro stuff as well.

I have lots of restoration projects in the queue so expect frequent videos.

Thanks for watching and please subscribe!
